{"tid":2298672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華深圳拍戲疑演抗疫片扮醫生　現場有「武漢醫院」搭景","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T13:46:18.000Z","uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":242,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"995f9bf61ef1f44cc2ef43322239e1aea50c8dbe","tid":2298672,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201123/407605510645223424216394.jpeg/aR0xntzTdGHKE8TQE23V-3dMslvqj59LjEAMsoxADLI?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201123%2F407605510645223424216394.jpeg%2FaR0xntzTdGHKE8TQE23V-3dMslvqj59LjEAMsoxADLI%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=1c5b254d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日有網民在深圳偶遇劉德華在街頭拍戲，見他戴住口罩並穿上醫生服飾，現場仲有「武漢市第四人民醫院」的搭景，相信拍攝新冠肺炎相關題材電影。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，劉德華到深圳完成14天後，近日正式為新片開工，見他穿上全副醫護人員的裝扮，相信扮演一名抗疫醫生，另外仲有一個恤衫配西褲的造型，同樣戴上口罩，神色凝重地在街上徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n早前片商宣布開拍首部抗疫片《中國醫生》，由劉偉強執導、張涵予及李晨等人主演，根據百度百科的劇情簡介，「本片根據2020年抗擊新冠肺炎疫情真實事件改編。講述全國各地的白衣逆行者在這場浩大戰役中紛紛挺身而出、爭分奪秒、浴血奮戰在武漢前線,不顧自身安危守護國人生命安全的震撼故事」，未知劉德華所拍攝的是否同一部作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201123/407605034109374464109536.jpeg/2-7p0FCdlAyqFNJ5umq8VZ814m_PWuGbo7PFSKOzxUg?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201123%2F407605034109374464109536.jpeg%2F2-7p0FCdlAyqFNJ5umq8VZ814m_PWuGbo7PFSKOzxUg%3Fv%3Dw960&h=550ac4e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff9a5a9fcfb9c2a50e41629e4dd7a27ebd65c587","tid":2298672,"uid":212249,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"01唔貼link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757b1fb655bfcc0a4ec12f91846c75629a688747","tid":2298672,"uid":34935,"like":171,"dislike":0,"score":171,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"支那又黎白事當紅事辦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dece01c2d4618546236abd9bbcccffe0b33ea764","tid":2298672,"uid":4811,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"可不可不要這麼樣，徘徊在目光內⋯<br />\n你會察覺到佢對人仔饑渴難耐"},{"pid":"aebfa0057215f1c5930fecbf6bed3ef540028732","tid":2298672,"uid":184801,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"填海華 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c213acb6cd9216146fce71371fb868de8001560c","tid":2298672,"uid":14065,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"扮李文亮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb85844aa045aad2cd0f5cee452ba2bb29c505b","tid":2298672,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"中招死埋佢啦老餅華"},{"pid":"1f300acb6119bc1a037e4340366b3fe6b56c545b","tid":2298672,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"樣辦戲"},{"pid":"13acfddc1221655b32ae4bec74be6e76f51614ea","tid":2298672,"uid":231908,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"c213acb6cd9216146fce71371fb868de8001560c","tid":2298672,"uid":14065,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"扮李文亮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/dPk89tRg_O8nUuAGck1QAiInI7_lKpuLZUuf6TJpUEBhAkyZrSERkmB8kggvdiMM72HUW9di9XNJw6WnrafcmBeB8lwt-H3JcIaKf-SNOA3qhqEG5k8Bm3_FlFKL\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FdPk89tRg_O8nUuAGck1QAiInI7_lKpuLZUuf6TJpUEBhAkyZrSERkmB8kggvdiMM72HUW9di9XNJw6WnrafcmBeB8lwt-H3JcIaKf-SNOA3qhqEG5k8Bm3_FlFKL&h=74ea4906&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a39ac0bedeefc2b07ea3dcd